    <h1>Module Name: k_res_partner_viber</h1>
    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>
        The module adds a Viber button next to the phone number, allowing users to easily initiate a conversation in Viber with the given phone number.
    </p>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Integration with Viber</li>
        <li>Displaying a Viber button next to phone numbers</li>
        <li>Clicking the button opens a chat in Viber with the respective phone number</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Screenshots</h2>
    <h3>Screenshot 1: Viber Button</h3>
    <img src="/k_res_partner_viber/static/description/v1.jpg" alt="Screenshot 1" width="600">
    <h3>Screenshot 2: Viber Chat</h3>
    <img src="/k_res_partner_viber/static/description/v2.jpg" alt="Screenshot 2" width="600">
    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <p>
        To install this module, follow the steps below:
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>Go to the Apps menu in your Odoo instance</li>
        <li>Click on the "Update Apps List" button</li>
        <li>Search for the "k_res_partner_viber" module</li>
        <li>Click on the "Install" button to install the module</li>
    </ol>
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <p>
        After installing the module, the Viber button will be displayed next to phone numbers in relevant views. Clicking the button will open a chat in Viber with the respective phone number.
    </p>
    <h2>Requirements</h2>
    <p>
        This module requires Odoo version 16 or later.
    </p>
